               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Collection of miniatures (sǝnsul):&#xD;
I-1) An equestrian saint  (section 1r)&#xD;
I-2) St Mar Bǝḥnam (section 2r)&#xD;
I-3) Shepherds (section 3r)&#xD;
I-4) King Herod killing the children (section 4r)&#xD;
I-5) Mothers of the killed children (section 5r)&#xD;
I-6) Six saints (section 6r)&#xD;
I-7) Three saints (section 7r)&#xD;
I-8) Three saints (section 8r)&#xD;
I-9) St Theodore (section 9r)&#xD;
I-10) Baptism of Jesus (section 10r)&#xD;
I-11) King David playing the harp (section 11r)&#xD;
&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 1 miracles (sections 12v-5v)</summary>
